                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para> However, variation exists in implementations due to various
                                networks, communication channels, set of transformations, and
                                different organizations of clinical data that currently exist.
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para> Part of the problem is expression-logic, part of the problem is
                                terminology. </para>
                            <itemizedlist>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>To assist, there are standards, and DCMs, but variation
                                        exists here in</para>
